preference.name: ARM_tcfs_import_file
preference.preference_description: Enables or suppresses performance monitoring of FMS file import operations in the Teamcenter server. Valid Values: ON to enable performance monitoring of FMS file import operations in the Teamcenter server. OFF to suppress performance monitoring of FMS file import operations in the Teamcenter server. This is the default value. The preference scope is All (the value can also be supplied using an enviromnent variable).
